 "text": "\nI have created a port for the unpost program. This program can extract\nbinary files from multi-segment uuencoded USENET postings or Email.\nAlthough, some news readers can do this also, it is still usefull if\nyou have a large collection of unsorted files (like a news spool\ndirectory for alt.binaries.*). The program is also reasonable smart\nin finding out which segments belong together\n\nTwo remarks:\n\n1) Have a look at the copyright notice in unpost.1, I'm not sure if an\n   entry in LEGAL is necessary.\n\n2) There is only a formatted manpage, I'm not sure if I handled this\n   correctly in the Makefile\n\nFrank\n\nbegin 644 unpost.tar\nM=6YP;W-T+P``````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM`````````````\"`T,#\u003cU-2``(\"`@,S0R(``@(\"`@(#`@`\"`@(\"`@(\"`@(\"`P\nM(\"`V-#,S,#4S-30Q(\"`Q,#4U,``@-0``````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM``````````````````````````````````````````!U\u003cW1A\u003cB`@`'9O;\u00268`\nM````````````````````````````````````=VAE96P`````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM``````````````````````!U;G!O\u003cW0O36%K969I;\u00264`````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````,3`P-C0T(``@(\"`S-#(@`\"`@\nM(\"`@,\"``(\"`@(\"`@(#$P,#(@(#8T,S,P-3$S,C(@(#$R,C\u003cQ`\"`P````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM`````'5S=\u0026%R(\"``=F]L9@````````````````````````````````````!W\nM:\u00265E;```````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````\nM``````````````